{"tid":1771850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友話今年聖誕節唔洗禮物同大餐","createTime":"2019-12-06T07:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T10:14:01.000Z","uid":93078,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17892737baa2e0231089b5afbeffe48e155ab8bd","tid":1771850,"uid":93078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月個人冇乜錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收入收咗 支出又多咗<br />\n難得女友不離不棄<br />\n所以做男友既點都好 都要諗辨法同佢慶祝聖誕 食聖誕大餐<br />\n<br />\n琴日我問佢今年聖誕想要咩禮物<br />\n同話佢知想帶佢去邊到食大餐 唔洗錫住我荷包<br />\n點知佢語重心長咁同我講 叫我今年唔洗大搞<br />\n簡簡單單果日食餐飯就可以 最重要係可以一齊<br />\n不如留返筆錢 將筆錢捐比星火 幫下小朋友<br />\n我聽到即刻感動到喊咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n唔知前世做咗咩好事 今世有個咁好既女友<br />\n女朋友我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位星期日見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a819876cf17a2920c220589205fa0468eb3c9073","tid":1771850,"uid":314531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"你女朋友就好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83735bfb5401bb7c4b6c8ef1d2870a9d506ae010","tid":1771850,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"無女朋友表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c2fc4c4254ee071992ca6bca656d2c673267ad","tid":1771850,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"你就好啦"},{"pid":"6463aa2deb55fcfca6e3248fac3aff0dac3232a7","tid":1771850,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"好善良 好識體貼人<br />\n唔自私 識感恩手足付出<br />\n<br />\n但樓主有錢記住多多少少補返 唔好唔找數 佢咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2469ced3bfb760a062191c891d9d5bc1660148","tid":1771850,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"我女朋友都好體貼架 <br />\n我出世咁多